    <h1>Near Me Searches</h1>
    <p class="description">Location-based queries where users add proximity language to find businesses immediately nearby. <strong>76% of searchers visit a business within 24 hours</strong> — the highest purchase intent in all of local search.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
