          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Why don't I show up for near me searches?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Common causes include: incomplete or unverified Google Business Profile, incorrect business address, too few Google reviews compared to competitors, inconsistent NAP across directories, or your business location being too far from the searcher. Fix GBP completeness first — it is the highest-leverage lever for near me visibility.</p></div></div>
